布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀在感人至深的致敬中称肖恩·麦高恩为“我一直以来最喜欢的作家之一” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-calls-shane-macgowan-one-of-my-all-time-favourite-writers-in-touching-tribute-3552221?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀向肖恩·麦高恩致敬，这是我最喜欢的作家之一Alex RigottiSat, 02 Dec 2023 10:08:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3552221 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀和肖恩·麦高恩（Jason Mendez/Martyn Goodacre/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Pogues 主唱于 11 月 30 日去世，享年 65 岁</p><p>布鲁斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-calls-shane-macgowan-one-of-my-all-time-favourite-writers-in-touching-tribute-3552221">·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 称肖恩·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 为“我一直以来最喜欢的作家之一”，这篇感人至深的致敬文章</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀和肖恩·麦高恩（Jason Mendez/Martyn Goodacre/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Springsteen-MacGowan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shane-macgowan">肖恩·麦高恩（Shane MacGowan）</a>去世的消息传出后，写了一篇感人至深的悼文。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/shane-macgowan-obituary-the-pogues-3551303">Shane MacGowan，1957-2023：一位不妥协、混乱的人</a></strong></li></ul><p>11月30日， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pogues">The Pogues</a>主唱MacGowan宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-shane-macgowan-has-died-aged-65-3551301">在家人和朋友的陪伴下安详地去世</a>。到目前为止， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-hails-bulletproof-shane-macgowan-as-one-of-the-best-lyricists-of-the-last-30-or-40-years-3552035">皮特·多尔蒂 (Pete Doherty)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-pens-heartfelt-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-and-sinead-oconnor-3552218">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave)</a>等人都向 MacGowan 致敬 - 可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-shane-macgowan-has-died-aged-65-3551301">在此处</a>找到持续的致敬列表。</p><p>现在，斯普林斯汀在社交媒体上分享的一篇帖子中写下了自己对这位标志性歌手的敬意：“在 E 街，我们对肖恩·麦高恩的去世感到心碎。”</p><p> “肖恩是我一直以来最喜欢的作家之一，”他继续说道。 “他的音乐和歌词的激情和深沉的强度是摇滚经典中最好的作品无法比拟的。”</p><p>他还分享了五月份在都柏林最后一次见到这位广受好评的歌手的回忆， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-surprises-shane-macgowan-with-visit-ahead-of-dublin-shows-3439380">当时他在该市的头条演出前让麦高恩感到惊讶</a>。 “上次我们在都柏林时，我很幸运能与肖恩和他可爱的妻子维多利亚一起度过一段时光，”他写道。 “他病得很重，但他的内心和精神仍然美丽。</p><p> “他的音乐是永恒的。我不知道我们其他人的情况如何，但 100 年后他们还会唱肖恩的歌曲。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0U3JgYv3Ee/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaig